### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

###

### --- Customers ---

### Create a customer
POST http://localhost:8080/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "email": "contact@acme.example",
  "phone": "+1-555-0100"
}

### List customers
GET http://localhost:8080/customers

### Get customer by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/customers/1

###

### --- Products ---

### Create a product
POST http://localhost:8080/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "WIDGET-001",
  "name": "Standard Widget",
  "priceCents": 1999,
  "active": true
}

### List products
GET http://localhost:8080/products

### Update a product
PATCH http://localhost:8080/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priceCents": 2499
}

###

### --- Orders ---

### Create an order
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "status": "DRAFT"
}

### Add item to order
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/1/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "qty": 2,
  "unitPriceCents": 1999
}

### Confirm an order
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/1/confirm

### List orders by status
GET http://localhost:8080/orders?status=DRAFT

###

### --- Inventory ---

### Get inventory
GET http://localhost:8080/inventory

### Adjust inventory
POST http://localhost:8080/inventory/1/adjust
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adjustment": 50
}
